### Documents API 调试文件
### 使用方式：
### 1. 先启动数据库并执行迁移：pnpm migrate:api
### 2. 启动 API：pnpm dev:api
### 3. 先执行 Login，后续请求会复用 login 返回的 accessToken。

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@email = demo@example.com
@password = password123
@deviceName = Local HTTP Client

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}",
  "deviceName": "{{deviceName}}"
}

### Create Root Document
# @name createRoot
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "My First Document",
  "icon": "📄"
}

### Create Child Document
# @name createChild
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentId": "{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}",
  "title": "Child Document"
}

### Get Document Tree
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/tree
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Get Document Detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Get Document Content
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}/content
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Update Document Content
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}/content
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "manual-test-block",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "props": {
        "textColor": "default",
        "backgroundColor": "default",
        "textAlignment": "left"
      },
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Hello from BlockNote content API",
          "styles": {}
        }
      ],
      "children": []
    }
  ]
}

### Update Document Metadata
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Document Title",
  "isStarred": true
}

### Archive Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}/archive
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Get Trash
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/trash
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Restore Document
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}/restore
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}

### Delete Document Permanently
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/documents/{{createRoot.response.body.$.data.id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.$.data.tokens.accessToken}}
